Class DefineMorphShapeTag

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICharacterReferrer, ICharacterTag, ITag
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefineMorphShape2Tag

    public class DefineMorphShapeTag
extends CharacterTag
implements ICharacterReferrer
    Represents a DefineMorphShapeTag tag in a SWF file.

    The DefineMorphShape tag defines the start and end states of a morph sequence. A morph object should be displayed with the PlaceObject2 tag, where the ratio field specifies how far the morph has progressed.
